docs {
  # List Shopping Lists
  
  Get all shopping lists for a family.
  
  ## Query Parameters
  
  None
  
  ## Response
  
  Returns an array of shopping lists, sorted by creation date (newest first).
  
  Each shopping list contains:
  - `_id`: Unique identifier
  - `familyId`: ID of the family
  - `name`: Shopping list name
  - `tags`: Array of tags
  - `items`: Array of items with:
    - `_id`: Item identifier
    - `name`: Item name
    - `checked`: Boolean indicating if item is marked as purchased
    - `createdAt`: Item creation timestamp
  - `createdBy`: ID of the user who created it
  - `createdAt`: Creation timestamp
  - `updatedAt`: Last update timestamp
  
  ## Status Codes
  
  - `200`: Shopping lists retrieved successfully
  - `401`: Unauthorized (missing or invalid token)
  - `403`: Forbidden (not a family member)
}
